+//! ├── fetch/      # Download (PyPI API, wheel selection, parallel)
+//! ├── install/    # Extract & verify (wheel, tarball)
+//! ├── link/       # Native linking (.so/.dylib/.dll tree-shaking)
+//! └── analyze/    # Import scanning, usage analysis
+//! ```
+
